Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:03.12,Default JP,,0,0,0,,私に会いに来たの？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:03.12,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你是來見我的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:06.22,Default JP,,0,0,0,,分からない...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:06.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我不知道...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:07.82,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ただ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:07.82,Default CN,,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:11.37,Default JP,,0,0,0,,僕は  どこで生まれたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:11.37,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我是在哪裡出生的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:13.69,Default JP,,0,0,0,,僕は  一体......
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:13.69,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我到底...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:22.27,Default JP,,0,0,0,,われらが闇の支配者がお目覚めになる日も
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:22.27,Default CN,,0,0,0,,看來 我們無須再等太久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:24.40,Default JP,,0,0,0,,そう遠いことではなさそうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:24.40,Default CN,,0,0,0,,黑暗的支配者就會覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:25.47,Default JP,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:25.47,Default CN,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:29.71,Default JP,,0,0,0,,いずれにしても  あのお方の意志を邪魔するものは  排除しておくべきか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:29.71,Default CN,,0,0,0,,無論情況如何 我們都將為那位大人排除一切阻礙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:39.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,それは絶対に行くべきよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:39.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,那肯定要去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:39.51,Default JP,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:39.51,Default CN,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:44.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,私ね  ヨーロッパに留学するのが  ずっと前からの夢だったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:44.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,去歐洲留學是我一直以來都嚮往的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:46.17,Default JP,,0,0,0,,でも
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:46.17,Default CN,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:49.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,親は「留学なんてまだ早い  絶対駄目だ」って言うの...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:49.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我父母都說“現在留學還太早 絕不會放你去”...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.32,Default JP,,0,0,0,,そうだったの...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.32,Default CN,,0,0,0,,這樣啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:54.57,Default JP,,0,0,0,,私にしてみたら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:54.57,Default CN,,0,0,0,,在我看來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:57.62,Default JP,,0,0,0,,両親と一緒に  パリに住めるなんて  夢みたいな話よ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:57.62,Default CN,,0,0,0,,能和父母一起生活在巴黎 就像是做夢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:00.07,Default JP,,0,0,0,,どうせ行くなら  若いうちに行って
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:00.07,Default CN,,0,0,0,,反正 要去就趁年輕趕緊去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:02.12,Default JP,,0,0,0,,沢山刺激を受けたほうがいいと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:02.12,Default CN,,0,0,0,,多經歷一些沒壞處
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.65,Default JP,,0,0,0,,だから  ほのかは絶対行くべきよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.65,Default CN,,0,0,0,,所以 你必須去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:07.10,Default JP,,0,0,0,,そんなチャンス  滅多にないもの！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:07.10,Default CN,,0,0,0,,這種機會可不常有啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.55,Default JP,,0,0,0,,それは  そのとおりなんだけど...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.55,Default CN,,0,0,0,,話是這麼說啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:16.65,Default JP,,0,0,0,,もっと速く！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:16.65,Default CN,,0,0,0,,再快一點！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:17.82,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ダッシュ  ダッシュ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:17.82,Default CN,,0,0,0,,跑起來跑起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.15,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ほのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.15,Default CN,,0,0,0,,穗乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:24.10,Default JP,,0,0,0,,どうしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:24.10,Default CN,,0,0,0,,有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:26.57,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ううん  ちょっと見に来ただけ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:26.57,Default CN,,0,0,0,,沒有 只是來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.55,Default JP,,0,0,0,,次の試合  もうすぐなんでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.55,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你們很快就要打下一場比賽了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:30.85,Default JP,,0,0,0,,...あのさ  ほのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:30.85,Default CN,,0,0,0,,...那個 穗乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.10,0:10:34.80,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ほのか  いつも言ってるじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.10,0:10:34.80,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你不是一直都這麼說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:37.75,Default JP,,0,0,0,,「自分のことは  自分で決めなきゃ」って
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:37.75,Default CN,,0,0,0,,“自己的事要自己來決定”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:40.70,Default JP,,0,0,0,,だから...その...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:40.70,Default CN,,0,0,0,,所以...就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.62,Default JP,,0,0,0,,うまく言えないんだけど...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.62,Default CN,,0,0,0,,可能我講得比較亂...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:44.55,Default JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}なぎさ  次どうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:44.55,Default CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}渚 接下來要幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:45.57,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あっ  うん！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:45.57,Default CN,,0,0,0,,啊 知道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:46.75,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待って
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:46.75,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:48.25,Default JP,,0,0,0,,早く  早く  早く！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:48.25,Default CN,,0,0,0,,趕緊的趕緊的趕緊的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:50.10,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ごめん  ほのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:50.10,Default CN,,0,0,0,,抱歉 穗乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:51.42,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あとで  おうちに寄っていい？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:51.42,Default CN,,0,0,0,,晚點我可以去一趟你家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:52.84,Default JP,,0,0,0,,続きは  そのときまた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:52.84,Default CN,,0,0,0,,到那時候我再繼續跟你講
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.60,Default JP,,0,0,0,,うん  こっちこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.60,Default CN,,0,0,0,,嗯 該道歉的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.42,Default JP,,0,0,0,,練習の邪魔して  ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.42,Default CN,,0,0,0,,打擾你們訓練了 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:10:57.25,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ううん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:10:57.25,Default CN,,0,0,0,,沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:10:57.76,Default JP,,0,0,0,,じゃあね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:10:57.76,Default CN,,0,0,0,,回見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:05.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ほのか  いつも言ってるじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:05.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你不是一直都這麼說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:09.22,Default JP,,0,0,0,,「自分のことは  自分で決めなきゃ」って
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:09.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,“自己的事要自己來決定”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:12.15,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎさの言うとおりなんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:12.15,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚說的也有道理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:13.22,Default JP,,0,0,0,,だけど...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:13.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:14.69,Default JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ほのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:14.69,Default CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}穗乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:16.42,Default JP,,0,0,0,,はい？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:16.42,Default CN,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:18.67,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎささんが  いらっしゃいましたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:18.67,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚來做客了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:23.40,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎさ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:23.40,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:24.85,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ごめんね...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:24.85,Default CN,,0,0,0,,對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:26.79,Default JP,,0,0,0,,何が？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:26.79,Default CN,,0,0,0,,為什麼道歉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:30.09,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なんか...いろいろ  勝手なこと言っちゃって...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:30.09,Default CN,,0,0,0,,就...感覺自己太張口就來了...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:31.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,そんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:31.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.32,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎさの気持ち  よく分かってるし
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.32,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我明白你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.45,0:11:36.59,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎさに言われたこと  そのとおりだと思うもの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.45,0:11:36.59,Default CN,,0,0,0,,而且 你說的也很有道理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:38.06,Default JP,,0,0,0,,本当？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:38.06,Default CN,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:38.97,Default JP,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:38.97,Default CN,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.43,Default JP,,0,0,0,,よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.43,Default CN,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:44.97,Default JP,,0,0,0,,...あのさ  ほのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:44.97,Default CN,,0,0,0,,...我說 穗乃香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:49.51,Default JP,,0,0,0,,こんなとき  気がきかないって思われるかもしれないけど...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:49.51,Default CN,,0,0,0,,可能你會嫌我神經太大條 不看場合吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:51.45,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あの...その...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:51.45,Default CN,,0,0,0,,呃...那什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:52.85,Default JP,,0,0,0,,うまく言えないんだけど...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:52.85,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我也不知道該怎麼說...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:54.37,Default JP,,0,0,0,,つまり...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:54.37,Default CN,,0,0,0,,就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:55.80,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎさ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:55.80,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:11:59.30,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ねぇ  ほのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:11:59.30,Default CN,,0,0,0,,對了 穗乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.49,Default JP,,0,0,0,,キャッチボールしようか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.49,Default CN,,0,0,0,,來玩接發球吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:03.37,Default JP,,0,0,0,,キャッチボール？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:03.37,Default CN,,0,0,0,,接發球？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.76,Default JP,,0,0,0,,いくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.76,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我要發了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:13.62,Default JP,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:13.62,Default CN,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:15.29,Default JP,,0,0,0,,そーれ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:15.29,Default CN,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:21.62,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ナイスキャッチ  ほのか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:21.62,Default CN,,0,0,0,,接得很棒啊 穗乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.12,Default JP,,0,0,0,,今度はパスね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.12,Default CN,,0,0,0,,現在輪到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:24.07,Default JP,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:24.07,Default CN,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:25.07,Default JP,,0,0,0,,じゃあ  いくわね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:25.07,Default CN,,0,0,0,,那 我要發了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:25.95,Default JP,,0,0,0,,それ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:25.95,Default CN,,0,0,0,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:33.22,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:33.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:33.77,Default JP,,0,0,0,,凄い
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:33.77,Default CN,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.07,0:12:36.90,Default JP,,0,0,0,,だてにキャプテンやってないからね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.07,0:12:36.90,Default CN,,0,0,0,,要是沒這點本事 可當不了隊長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:38.45,Default JP,,0,0,0,,いくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:38.45,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我要發了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:39.55,Default JP,,0,0,0,,それ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:39.55,Default CN,,0,0,0,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:01.40,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ねぇ  なぎさ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:01.40,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我說 渚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:02.12,Default JP,,0,0,0,,うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:02.12,Default CN,,0,0,0,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:05.90,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ふたりでキャッチボールするなんて  初めてだね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:05.90,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我們兩人還是第一次這樣玩接發球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:07.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:07.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:15.51,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なんか  体動かすのって  楽しい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:15.51,Default CN,,0,0,0,,這麼活動一下身體 感覺還蠻開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:19.35,Default JP,,0,0,0,,でしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:19.35,Default CN,,0,0,0,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:20.75,Default JP,,0,0,0,,よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:20.75,Default CN,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.67,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ふたりとも  元気になって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.67,Default CN,,0,0,0,,兩人都變得精神起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:23.81,Default JP,,0,0,0,,よかったポポ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:23.81,Default CN,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:27.15,Default JP,,0,0,0,,遠いところへ行く話は  どうなったメポ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:27.15,Default CN,,0,0,0,,可是 去巴黎的事就這麼晾著不提了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:29.07,Default JP,,0,0,0,,よく分からないミポ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:29.07,Default CN,,0,0,0,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:32.80,Default JP,,0,0,0,,だけど  ほのかが元気になってくれることが  一番ミポ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:32.80,Default CN,,0,0,0,,但是 穗乃香能打起精神來比什麼都好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:34.80,Default JP,,0,0,0,,一番ルル~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:34.80,Default CN,,0,0,0,,比什麼都好~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:36.27,Default JP,,0,0,0,,やめるポポ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:36.27,Default CN,,0,0,0,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:39.34,Default CN,,0,0,0,,太好了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.46,Default JP,,0,0,0,,やっぱりよくないメポ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.46,Default CN,,0,0,0,,果然不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:43.52,Default JP,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:43.52,Default CN,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:45.55,Default JP,,0,0,0,,邪悪な気配を感じるメポ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:45.55,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我感受到了邪惡的氣息！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:48.39,Default JP,,0,0,0,,なぎさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:48.39,Default CN,,0,0,0,,渚！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:49.17,Default JP,,0,0,0,,うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:49.17,Default CN,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:53.82,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ありがとう！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:53.82,Default CN,,0,0,0,,謝謝你！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:55.47,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:55.47,Default CN,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:13:58.70,Default JP,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:13:58.70,Default CN,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.12,Default JP,,0,0,0,,楽しそうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.12,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你們玩得很開心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:04.37,Default JP,,0,0,0,,何するのよ？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:04.37,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你想幹嘛？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:08.40,Default JP,,0,0,0,,所詮  お前達の運命は  このボールと同じ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:08.40,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你們的命運啊 就跟這球一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:10.10,Default JP,,0,0,0,,今すぐ握り潰してやろう！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:10.10,Default CN,,0,0,0,,看我現在就來捏碎你們吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:11.98,Default JP,,0,0,0,,何言ってるメポ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:11.98,Default CN,,0,0,0,,口氣不小啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:13.90,Default JP,,0,0,0,,冗談じゃないわよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:13.90,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你想得美！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:14.77,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ほのか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:14.77,Default CN,,0,0,0,,穗乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:15.80,Default JP,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:15.80,Default CN,,0,0,0,,嗯
